title: Ep. 65: Divisional-Round Preview With Terez Paylor
description:
The Ringer's Robert Mays and Danny Kelly discuss the Seahawks visiting the Falcons (01:26), the Patriots hosting the Texans (16:21), and Aaron Rodgers and Green Bay going to Dallas (25:38). Then Terez Paylor of The Kansas City Star joins the show to break down the Chiefs' matchup against the Steelers (37:29).
